# Aria Plugin 版本信息

> **版本**: 1.3.2
> **发布日期**: 2026-02-06
> **仓库**: https://forgejo.10cg.pub/10CG/aria-plugin

## 版本号

```
1.3.2
```

## 说明

- **Major (1)**: 稳定核心架构，十步循环 + OpenSpec 规范
- **Minor (3)**: 25 个 Skills，TDD Enforcer v2.0 文档驱动重构，Brainstorm Skill v2.0.0
- **Patch (2)**: state-scanner 跨平台指南 + brainstorm 对话控制重构

## 包含内容

### Skills (25个)

**十步循环核心 (9个)**
- state-scanner, workflow-runner, phase-a-planner, phase-b-developer
- phase-c-integrator, phase-d-closer, spec-drafter, task-planner, progress-updater

**协作思考 (1个)**
- brainstorm

**Git 工作流 (4个)**
- commit-msg-generator, strategic-commit-orchestrator, branch-manager, branch-finisher

**开发工具 (3个)**
- subagent-driver, agent-router, tdd-enforcer

**架构文档 (5个)**
- arch-common, arch-search, arch-update, arch-scaffolder, api-doc-generator

**需求管理 (3个)**
- requirements-validator, requirements-sync, forgejo-sync

### Agents (10个)

- tech-lead, context-manager, knowledge-manager
- backend-architect, mobile-developer, qa-engineer
- ai-engineer, api-documenter, ui-ux-designer, legal-advisor

### Hooks 系统

- SessionStart → state-scanner
- SessionEnd → progress-updater
- PreToolUse → tdd-enforcer

